high_descs: Walk forward to the chairs, then turn right, walk forward and turn left at the statue, then walk to the vase on the dining table.
Pick up the small, top part of the vase from the dining table.
Turn right, walk forward to the statue, then turn right and walk to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a piece of a vase by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Walk from the living room to the dining table on the laptop's side.
Grab the right blue vase off the table.
Walk from the dining table to the left seat.
Turn on the lamp on the left of the seat.
anns.task_desc: Grab a vase from the dining table and examine the vase under a lamp's light.

high_descs: Walk straight to the chairs. Turn right walk to the table and turn left. Walk straight to the table turn left to the trash can and make a right. Walk halfway and turn to face the middle of the table.
Pick up the blue round object closest to you on the table.
Turn right walk to the wall. Turn left take a few steps then turn right. Walk to the table and turn right. Walk straight to the TV make a right. Raise the object until it is level with the lamp.
anns.task_desc: To retrieve the blue object to hold up against the lamp.
